    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Android Studio - Github PagerSlidingTabStrip Project Build Error]]></title>
    <link href="http://shaching.github.io/2014/07/11/android-studio-github-pagerslidingtabstrip-project-build-error/"/>
    <updated>2014-07-11T18:57:58+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://shaching.github.io/2014/07/11/android-studio-github-pagerslidingtabstrip-project-build-error</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I imported Github PagerSlidingTabStrip project into Android Studio 0.8.2.</p>

<p>Oops. And it wasted me a lot of time to fix build error.</p>

<p>To avoid encountered the same problems.</p>

<p>I noted solutions here and hoped this can help you. :)</p>

<!--more -->


<h3>Build Error 1.</h3>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>Error:Build script error, unsupported Gradle DSL method found: 'getBootClasspath()'!
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>Possible causes could be:
</span><span class='line'>  - you are using Gradle version where the method is absent Fix Gradle settings
</span><span class='line'>  - you didn't apply Gradle plugin which provides the method Apply Gradle plugin
</span><span class='line'>  - or there is a mistake in a build script Goto source</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Modified PagerSlidingTabStrip / build.gradle.</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>---classpath 'com.android.tools.build:gradle:0.6.+'
</span><span class='line'>+++classpath 'com.android.tools.build:gradle:0.12.+'
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Modified PagerSlidingTabStrip / gradle / wrapper / gradle-wrapper.properties</p>

